://web02.multicomnet.local/cartoes/wp-content/uploads/Tela61.png\" width=\"1005\" height=\"626\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1188\" alt=\"Tela7\" src=\"http://web02.multicomnet.local/cartoes/wp-content/uploads/Tela71-1024x435.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"435\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1189\" alt=\"Tela8\" src=\"http://web02.multicomnet.local/cartoes/wp-content/uploads/Tela81-1024x449.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"449\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1189\" alt=\"Tela8\" src=\"http://web02.multicomnet.local/cartoes/wp-content/uploads/Tela81-1024x449.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"449\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Obs:</strong> Lembrando que você será cobrado mensalmente pelo método recorrente.\r\n\r\nDepois leia os <strong>Termos e Condições</strong>. Aceitando marque a opção e <strong>Finalize seu Pedido.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1190\" alt=\"Tela9\" src=\"http://web02.multicomnet.local/cartoes/wp-content/uploads/Tela91-1024x541.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"541\" /></a>", "Como Comprar", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "904-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-03-20 10:51:12", "2014-03-20 12:51:12", "", "904", "http://web02.multicomnet.local/cartoes/904-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
